  "texts": [
    "Based on Nanjing's road construction standards and actual road conditions, the data quality was ensured by retaining information on expressways, fast roads, main roads, secondary roads, national highways, and county roads, while excluding other road types.",
    "The data were processed to remove duplicate lines, floating lines, and internal dense lines.",
    "The centerlines of the roads were extracted, and a 55 m wide buffer zone was established as the foundational data for \"path\" map analysis and extraction.",
    "This study is based on the spatial cognitive structure framework of the five basic spatial elements of urban imagery (paths, nodes, landmarks, districts, and edges).",
    "It analyzes and extracts urban collective memory information from Weibo platform check-in data and maps it onto a spatial map (Fig. 3)."
